Package: 00-min
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends:
 aptitude,
 locales-all,
 mc,
 sudo,
 systemd-cron,
 vim,
 wget,
 ${misc:Depends},
Provides:
 nano,
Replaces:
 nano,
Description: Task for the minimal non-GUI system
 This is a task package installing minimal system without GUI.
 .
 This is meant to be used for creating the initial image for the minimal chroot
 and virtual system.

